kommentar: Welcome to this little data science project-planning app! This application is a template to test out an reactive background (mind at the bottom section below the background also interacts with your mouse). Also I build the app to display as many panels as there are projects found in the data. This means the code for the panel is only written once as a function. To add a bit of complexity, the assumption is, that every project has a similar structure of mile stones that are due in a fixed realtion to the start- and end-point.
